Interface Validator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmailValidator, PasswordValidator, UserNameValidator

    public interface Validator
    Provides the template for comparing user input to correct format. - Ryan 10/28/2018. Contains all methods for creating alert boxes both confirmation and error. -Ryan 11/15/2018. Date 10/28/2018
